### Test Student CRUD API

### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/students

### Get all students
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get student by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Create new student
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Cooper",
  "email": "alice.cooper@example.com",
  "age": 20,
  "grade": "A"
}

### Update student
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "grade": "A"
}

### Delete student
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/3

### Test validation - Invalid email
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid User",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "age": 20,
  "grade": "A"
}

### Test validation - Invalid grade
